      "content": "Letting go doesn't mean you'll suddenly find happiness or that your problems will magically disappear. It means surrendering to the fact that you're not in control, and that the pain and struggle are a part of your existence. It's about accepting that you're not capable of changing the world, and that sometimes, the only way to move forward is to stop trying. By letting go, you can finally release the burden of expectation and responsibility, and just... be.",
      "source": "target",
